Titolo: NBA In The Zone '98

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: NBA In The Zone '98 (also known as NBA Pro 98 in Australia and Europe) is a basketball game for the Nintendo 64 and PlayStation. It was released in 1998 and developed and published by Konami. The cover features Glen Rice of the Charlotte Hornets.
The game has a "Create a Player" section and a season/playoffs section. All players in the game are based on stats and rosters of the 1996-1997 NBA season.

Genere: Sports 

Valutazione: N/A
